query:
-- Count installments by status for Property #25
SELECT status, COUNT(*) as count, SUM(amount) as total_amount
FROM installments 
WHERE contractId = 210001
GROUP BY status;

-- Show first 10 installments
SELECT id, dueDate, amount, status
FROM installments 
WHERE contractId = 210001
ORDER BY dueDate ASC
LIMIT 10;
